{"tid":1255570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政情：建制陣營主張打「消耗戰」以平和及包容態度對待，相信行動不斷升級，民意總有轉向的一天。","createTime":"2019-06-24T14:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T14:41:55.000Z","uid":52609,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3802ba33f5a9844ce9e2826fcd1dc9ff7587e4","tid":1255570,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=352985&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352985%26refer%3DShare&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=9ce36170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D352985%26refer%3DShare&h=8ff8df28\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=352985&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n//至於如何「收科」，建制陣營都主張打「消耗戰」以平和及包容態度對待，相信對家行動不斷升級，民意總有轉向的一天。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多送中方法<br />\n廿三條、國歌法、明日大嶼、軍事碼頭、DQ....<br />\n擋得幾多條?<br />\n<br />\n要直搗核心，普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日大家都FEEL到民意散散地<br />\n出黎嘅人愈黎愈少<br />\n原因係有啲人收左貨、有啲人開始攰、無方向<br />\n<br />\n只有將運動提升到新一層次先可以再集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如89民運一開始都只係重新評價胡耀邦、反貪<br />\n到後來直搗核心，變成民主運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訴求升級 重提真普選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253933</a>"},{"pid":"c8340a5542ca66f4de2665ccb6ffb585682eab84","tid":1255570,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3U-78lVHOAE\" data-sr-url=\